# Project Architecture

## Monorepo Layout
- `infrastructure/` — AWS CDK stacks (IaC)
- `backend/src/functions/` — Lambda handlers (thin)
- `backend/src/services/` — Business logic and external integrations
- `backend/src/models/` — TypeScript types, Zod schemas, DTOs
- `backend/src/shared/` — Utilities, middleware, response helpers
- `frontend/` — React SPA

## Service Pattern (Adapter)
External integrations use an interface + implementation pattern:

```typescript
// services/acmasoft.ts — interface
export interface IAcmasoftService {
  buscarClientes(query: string): Promise<AcmasoftCliente[]>;
}

// services/acmasoft-mock.ts — mock implementation
export class AcmasoftMockService implements IAcmasoftService { ... }

// When real API exists, add:
// services/acmasoft-real.ts — real implementation
```

Instantiate via factory or env var toggle, never import implementation directly in handlers.

## DynamoDB Access
- Use `@aws-sdk/lib-dynamodb` (DocumentClient) for all DynamoDB operations
- Create one shared DynamoDB client in `shared/dynamo.ts`
- Table names come from environment variables

## Processing Pipeline
Remito flow: S3 Upload → Textract OCR (async) → Bedrock IA (Claude 3.5 Haiku) → Manual validation → Acmasoft
States: `procesando_ocr` → `pendiente_ia` → `pendiente_validacion` → `validado` → `enviado_acmasoft`
Errors: `error_ocr`, `error_ia`, `error_acmasoft`
